highlights.text: TENBLANK has the most spots on Viral Songs Taiwan. “旋律と結晶” is the highest at #3.
“DIA DELÍCIA” by Nakama and ΣP has been on Viral Songs Taiwan the longest, at 81 days straight.
“Hunting Soul” by トシロウ（CV.谷山紀章） is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Taiwan at #1.
“ovo” by L13 is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Taiwan, up 9 spots at #75.
